original_title: Brooklyn: New York Avenue (East) - Pacific Street
text:
1. East New York Ave. (right), north side, east of Pacific Street to Atlantic Ave., showing also the Long Island R.R. elevated and the Atlantic Ave. station. Shown on the left, are buildings on Pacific Street, which at this point becomes East New York Ave.

August 10, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.

2. East New York Ave., Pacific St. to Atlantic Ave. Neg. A-182
P.L. Sperr
July 24, 1941.
